The paper discusses the benchmarking of deep neural network architectures, which is a topic closely related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper proposes a synthetic benchmarking approach, which could also be relevant to the field of computer architecture (cs.AR).
